                <h1>How to Enable Dark Mode in Outlook</h1>
                <p>To enable Dark Mode in Outlook, open the application and navigate to the File menu. Select Options, then choose General. In the Personalize your copy of Microsoft Office section, find the Office Theme dropdown. Select 'Black' or 'Dark Gray' for a soothing dark interface. Don't forget to save changes!</p>
